name: FRESH
description:
These One-of-a-kind Earrings unite a coral tone bead with a swirl of shell.  A faceted crystal bead links the two in this design reminiscent of a calming yet exotic ocean shore.   

Pair these with a basic T n' jean to create a fresh look.

options.name: One size, one color, one pair.

name: Out of control!
description:
Okay, so this one's quiet intricate, so Imma keep this description as brief as I can! Okay, so the true-red bead, it's glass with all kinds of colors swirled into it - creamsicle, limes, blues, all that.  The bottom's blue faux pearl beads and faceted forest green lucite beads wrapped all around the blue one's to create something like a wheel.  Linking the two is a faceted diamond-shaped crystal bead.  

Theres a lot going on in these so, keep everything else simple.  Think Basic when you're look for something to wear with these earrings.  The outfit's the accessory when you where these crazy cool earrings!

name: The sky is blue; the water gleams.
description:
The extravagance of this pair begins with the hooks that hold delicate crystal beads. It continues with the sky and navy blue glass swirled to form delicate narrow bead.   A large faceted crystal bead rests atop a golden bouquet, which rests atop a navy blue porcelain bead.   

This is yet another that requires no more than a simple T or tank; it complements itself. Be adventures when choosing the T color - a yellow or a purple, green maybe.
